Information We Collect
There are three basic categories of information we collect:
Information you choose to give us
Information we get when you use our Services or Apps
Information we get from third parties.
Here's a little more detail on each of these categories.
Information You Choose to Give Us
When you interact with our Service or Apps, we collect the information that you choose to share with us. It probably goes without saying, but we'll say it anyway: When you contact customer support or communicate with us in any other way (e.g. commenting articles), we'll collect whatever information you volunteer.
Information We Get When You Use Our Services or Apps
When you use our Services or Apps, we collect information about which of those Services or Apps you've used and how you've used them. We might know, for instance, that you watched a particular page, saw a specific ad or used a feature. Here's a fuller explanation of the types of information we collect when you use our Services or Apps:
