In-app Purchases
Although the download of our Apps may be offered for free, some additional content can be purchased for real money inside Apps or Services. Such purchases do not always require the re-entry of credit card information because they may be made through an existing third-party account (such as a Microsoft, Google Play or iTunes account). If you do not want to use this feature, turn off in-app purchases in your device's settings. To learn how to disable in-app purchases, refer to the device manufacturer.
Some in-app purchases may be auto-renewable subscription based IAP which in simple terms means that:
Payment will be charged to your account (such as a Microsoft, Google Play or iTunes account) at confirmation of purchase and will automatically renew (at the duration/price selected) unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hrs before the end of the current period.
Account (such as a Microsoft, Google Play or iTunes account) will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period
Current subscription may not be cancelled during the active subscription period; however, you can manage your subscription and/or turn off auto-renewal by visiting your account settings (such as a Microsoft, Google Play or iTunes account) after purchase.
Any unused portion of the free one month initial period will be forfeited when you purchases a subscription.
Additional content is offered "as is" and by making in-app purchases you, or anyone using your device and/or credentials, are responsible for any financial transactions and you agree that We will not be held responsible for any loss, material or otherwise. We reserve the right to deny refunding requests for in-app purchases in cases of negligence to the terms stated here in this agreement.
Health and nutritional information
Apple Health / Google Health Connect. Our apps use the Apple Health / Google Health Connect service to improve apps functionality and provide you with better inapp services. The use of the Apple Health / Google Health Connect service is subject to your consent to the synchronization of data with the service in question. If you agree to data synchronization, you provide applications with information about your activities, such as running or doing other sports; calories burned and distance traveled; body characteristics such as weight, height, body fat percentage, waist circumference, blood pressure and glucose measurements; for the purpose of preparing the tracking of your activity in the application, keeping a diary of weight, pressure and glucose levels as well as preparation of statistics and graphs. Data obtained from the Apple Health / Google Health Connect service is stored on your device. If you use our data backup service, the application data is stored on our server until you delete it, which you can do from within the application.
Our apps do not use information gained through the use of the Apple Health / Google Health Connect service for advertising or similar services. We do not disclose any information gained through Apple Health or Google Health Connect frameworks to a third party without express permission from the user. We do not sell information gained through Apple Health or Google Health Connect frameworks to advertising platforms, data brokers, or information resellers. Only if the user consents we may share their Apple Health or Google Health Connect frameworks data with a third party for medical research.
In order to stop synchronization of your data with the Apple Health / Google Health Connect service, you can at any time disable data synchronization from the user profile level as indicated in the
Apple Health
or
Google Health Connect
documentation.
Sensitive User Data Access
Our app accesses specific health-related data, including blood pressure, heart rate, weight, and nutritional intake, to provide personalized health insights and recommendations.
Data Collection, Use, and Sharing
We collect and use your health data to enhance app functionality and improve user experience. Your data may be shared with healthcare providers only with your consent to facilitate better health management.
Data Usage Limitation
User data is exclusively used to provide app functionality. We do not use health data for advertising or unrelated purposes.
User Consent
Data access requires your explicit consent before collection or usage of the data.
Data Protection
We implement stringent security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, loss, or breach, ensuring your health information remains confidential and secure.
